---
---

<section class="section" id="about">
  <div class="container">
    <p class="section-label">ABOUT</p>
    <div class="about-grid">
      <!-- Left: Bio + Career -->
      <div class="about-left">
        <h2 class="section-title">문제를 정의하고<br />구조로 풀어냅니다</h2>
        <div class="quote-box">
          <p class="quote-text">
            사용자 리뷰 37,923건을 분석해 핵심 불만 요인을 구조화하고, 사용자 여정
            기반 개선안을 설계한 경험이 있습니다. 동시에 교육 상품 기획부터 AI
            파이프라인 설계까지 — 문제를 정의하고 작동하는 구조로 만드는 기획자입니다.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="career">
          <p class="career-label">CAREER</p>
          <div class="career-list">
            <div class="career-item">
              <span class="career-period">2024.05 — 2024.12</span>
              <div>
                <p class="career-company">패스트캠퍼스 (데이원컴퍼니)</p>
                <p class="career-role">콘텐츠 상품 기획자</p>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="career-item">
              <span class="career-period">2023.04 — 2025.06</span>
              <div>
                <p class="career-company">아른 사이</p>
                <p class="career-role">프로젝트 매니저 (사이드)</p>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="career-item">
              <span class="career-period">2021.01 — 2023.04</span>
              <div>
                <p class="career-company">살미달라</p>
                <p class="career-role">패션 브랜드 대표 / MD</p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="about-contact">
          <a href="mailto:seobgak11@naver.com" class="contact-link">seobgak11@naver.com</a>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Right: Stats 2x2 -->
      <div class="about-right">
        <div class="stats-grid">
          <div class="stat-card">
            <span class="sc-num">37,923건</span>
            <span class="sc-label">앱 리뷰 분석</span>
            <span class="sc-ctx">Gcar VoC 분석</span>
          </div>
          <div class="stat-card">
            <span class="sc-num">177%</span>
            <span class="sc-label">텀블벅 달성률</span>
            <span class="sc-ctx">아른 사이 크라우드펀딩</span>
          </div>
          <div class="stat-card">
            <span class="sc-num">29+</span>
            <span class="sc-label">자동 생성 피드</span>
            <span class="sc-ctx">AI 콘텐츠 생성 자동화</span>
          </div>
          <div class="stat-card">
            <span class="sc-num">4개</span>
            <span class="sc-label">콘텐츠 포맷</span>
            <span class="sc-ctx">영상·출판·교육·SNS</span>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="edu-box">
          <p class="edu-label">Education</p>
          <p class="edu-main">한림대학교</p>
          <p class="edu-sub">사학전공 · 광고홍보학과 — 2025.02 졸업</p>
          <div class="cert-row">
            <span class="chip">OPIc IH</span>
            <span class="chip">GTQ 1급</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .about-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 4rem;
    align-items: start;
    margin-top: 2rem;
  }

  /* Quote box */
  .quote-box {
    background: var(--c-canvas);
    border: 1px solid var(--c-hairline);
    border-left: 3px solid var(--c-ink);
    padding: 1rem 1.25rem;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
  }

  .quote-text {
    font-size: 0.875rem;
    color: var(--c-body);
    line-height: 1.7;
  }

  /* Career */
  .career-label {
    font-size: 0.6875rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.12em;
    color: var(--c-mute);
    text-transform: uppercase;
    margin-bottom: 0.875rem;
  }

  .career-list {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 0;
    border-top: 1px solid var(--c-hairline);
  }

  .career-item {
    display: flex;
    gap: 1.25rem;
    padding: 0.875rem 0;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--c-hairline);
  }

  .career-period {
    font-size: 0.75rem;
    color: var(--c-mute);
    white-space: nowrap;
    min-width: 140px;
    padding-top: 0.1rem;
    font-variant-numeric: tabular-nums;
  }

  .career-company {
    font-size: 0.875rem;
    font-weight: 500;
    color: var(--c-ink);
    margin-bottom: 0.15rem;
  }

  .career-role {
    font-size: 0.8125rem;
    color: var(--c-body);
  }

  .about-contact {
    margin-top: 1.5rem;
  }

  .contact-link {
    font-size: 0.8125rem;
    color: var(--c-sky);
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--c-sky-line);
    padding-bottom: 1px;
    transition: color var(--dur) var(--ease);
  }

  .contact-link:hover {
    color: var(--c-sky-deep);
  }

  /* Stats grid */
  .stats-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 1px;
    background: var(--c-hairline);
    border: 1px solid var(--c-hairline);
    margin-bottom: 1.25rem;
  }

  .stat-card {
    background: var(--c-canvas);
    padding: 1.25rem;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 0.2rem;
  }

  .sc-num {
    font-size: 1.625rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    letter-spacing: -0.025em;
    color: var(--c-sky-deep);
    line-height: 1.1;
  }

  .sc-label {
    font-size: 0.8125rem;
    color: var(--c-body);
  }

  .sc-ctx {
    font-size: 0.6875rem;
    color: var(--c-sky);
  }

  /* Education */
  .edu-box {
    background: var(--c-surface);
    padding: 1rem 1.25rem;
  }

  .edu-label {
    font-size: 0.6875rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.12em;
    color: var(--c-mute);
    text-transform: uppercase;
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }

  .edu-main {
    font-size: 0.9375rem;
    font-weight: 500;
    color: var(--c-ink);
    margin-bottom: 0.2rem;
  }

  .edu-sub {
    font-size: 0.8125rem;
    color: var(--c-body);
    margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
  }

  .cert-row {
    display: flex;
    gap: 0.5rem;
  }

  @media (max-width: 760px) {
    .about-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      gap: 2.5rem;
    }

    .career-period {
      min-width: 100px;
    }
  }
</style>
